  "subject": "Update sdl/core version in odlsli",
  "commit_message": "Update sdl/core version in odlsli\n\nUpdate odlsli container to use version 0.1.1-SNAPSHOT of sli/core to see\nif that resolves issue loading sliapi.  If this works, will submit\nchanges to roll all ccsdk sli components as well as ccsdk distribution\nto version 0.1.1-SNAPSHOT to keep versions in sync.\n\nChange-Id: I9e4c1e981ae9ee1a01ef8ca850503ca457f0d43a\nIssue-ID: CCSDK-69\nSigned-off-by: Dan Timoney <dtimoney@att.com>\n",
